article.description: — Hunter McIntosh had 23 points as Elon beat Campbell 66-56 on Wednesday.
article.headline: McIntosh scores 23 to carry Elon past Campbell 66-56
article.linkText: McIntosh scores 23 to carry Elon past Campbell 66-56
article.story: ELON, N.C. -- — Hunter McIntosh had 23 points as Elon beat Campbell 66-56 on Wednesday. Kris Wooten and Jerald Gillens-Butler added 12 points apiece for Elon (3-0). Hunter Woods had 11 points and seven rebounds. Jordan Whitfield had 14 points for the Fighting Camels (4-1). Cedric Henderson Jr. added 12 points and Gediminas Mokseckas had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
